You are examining a login issue for a user and you need to determine where their homedirectory is located. Within which file can you find their home directory?
A)  /etc/passwd
B)  /etc/homedirs
C)  /etc/user.conf
D)  /etc/defaults/user
A
A. The /etc/passwd file contains user information, including their home directory. Theother options are not valid.
